'''Swarnkar''' (alternately '''Sunar, Soni,''' '''Suniar,Sah,Verma,poddar'''(eh) and '''Sonar''') is a Hindu caste in [[India]] and [[Nepal]] referring to the community of people who work as goldsmiths.<ref>[http://www.webhostar.com/sonar/ Sonar community]</ref> Though the community is primarily Hindu, some members in the states of Haryana and Punjab are Sikh.

