The '''École Nationale Supérieure d'Agronomie et des Industries Alimentaires''' ('''ENSAIA''') is a [[France|French]] engineering school located in [[Vandoeuvre-lès-Nancy]] near [[Nancy, France|Nancy]] in the [[Meurthe-et-Moselle]] ''[[Departments of France|département]]'' that specialises in biological and agricultural engineering.

Students can enter the school by different ways, but the most common is by a two-year preparation class.

